data.description: Welcome to Calusa Ridge! This home is located in a prestigious gated community and also situated on a cul-de-sac,    an oversized lake lot and home to a tortoise preserve.The amenities that this home offers are abundant.  From a fully appointed kitchen with quartzite countertops, 20 inch porcelain tile, full marble master bathroom, HAGUE water softener and filter,  impact windows and doors, doors are 8 and 10 foot throughout, salt water Pentair automated electric heat pump, screened pool and spa with outside shower, upgraded wood trim, custom wiring with surround ceiling speakers, security system, SMART house automation, manicured professional landscape, this home has it all! Interested in exploring your culinary talents? The rear yard features a generous sized herb garden, perfect for any chef! The property is approximately 12 feet above sea level and no flood insurance is required.  This home is meticulously maintained and is move in ready!While relaxing by the pool you will enjoy the comforting sounds of egrets, our resident eagle and beautiful views of the lake and nature.If quiet island life with all the comforts of luxury living is what you are seeking, this is your new home!
